---
title: Tex-Mex Chorizo Bowls with Sour Cream and Feta
description: Tonight, tuck into this bowl of punchy Mexican-inspired flavours! Chorizo gets boosted by salsa and our Enchilada Spice Blend, while rice gets sautéed with bell peppers to give it a subtle sweetness. A dollop of zippy sour cream brings loads of flavour with little effort in the kitchen.
